query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(tq2 q2) NoHashJoin(q2 tq2 u2) NoHashJoin(q2 s2 t2 tq2 u1 u2 q1) NoHashJoin(q1 q2 s2 t2 tq2 u1 u2 s1) NoHashJoin(q1 q2 s1 s2 t2 tq2 u1 u2 t1) */ select account.display_name
from tag_question AS tq2
inner join question AS q2
on tq2.question_id = q2.id
inner join so_user AS u2
on q2.owner_user_id = u2.id AND q2.site_id = u2.site_id
inner join tag AS t2
on tq2.tag_id = t2.id AND t2.name = 'split'
inner join site AS s2
on t2.site_id = s2.site_id AND tq2.site_id = s2.site_id AND q2.site_id = s2.site_id AND s2.site_name = 'stackoverflow'
inner join so_user AS u1
on u1.account_id = u2.account_id
inner join question AS q1
on q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.site_id = u1.site_id
inner join site AS s1
on q1.site_id = s1.site_id AND s1.site_name = 'math'
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.site_id = s1.site_id AND t1.name = 'prime-numbers'
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on tq1.question_id = q1.id AND tq1.tag_id = t1.id AND tq1.site_id = s1.site_id
inner join account AS account
on account.id = u1.account_id;
